#include "toolbox_version.h"
Short: Utility for SCSI emulators
Author: daniel@malarhojden.nu (Daniel Lundqvist)
Uploader: daniel@malarhojden.nu (Daniel Lundqvist)
Version: MAKEVERSION(VERSION,REVISION)
Type: disk/misc
Architecture: m68k-amigaos >= 1.3

toolbox is a utility for SCSI emulators, such as ZuluSCSI and BlueSCSI.

See toolbox.guide for documentation.

Source is available at https://github.com/dlundqvist/toolbox.

Release 0.4
-----------
	- Fix return code in case of errors.
	- Add command to show connected WiFi network.
	- Add command to scan WiFi networks.
	- Indicate in file listings if file is larger than 4GiB.
	- Don't allow to GET files larger than or equal to 2GiB.
	- Fix output issue when downloading empty files.
	- Fixed incompatibilities with Kickstart 1.3.

Release 0.3
-----------
	- Support for path in GET action.
	- Better validation of command line arguments.
	- Documentation updates/adjustments.
	- Adjust output for LISTFILES action (dropped Index column).
	- CD index in LISTCDS and SETCD actions start with 1 instead of 0.

Release 0.2
-----------
	- Fix reading data for LISTDEVICES action.
	- Adjust and correct output for LISTDEVICES action.

Release 0.1
-----------
	- First release.
